00:25:49,800 --> 00:25:52,160
they'll have the goods all year round.

402
00:25:53,420 --> 00:25:56,200
I'll bring out the warabi mochi, that'll do!

403
00:25:56,700 --> 00:25:57,300
Yeah!

404
00:25:57,760 --> 00:25:59,280
I'll get Yusuke to help you.

405
00:25:59,380 --> 00:26:01,640
It's been a long time
since I've seen my husband smile

